panelURL: url to use for redirect for panel
dashboardURL: url to use for redirect for dashboard
editorURL: url to use for redirect for editor

database.db: ... (these settings are passed directly into rethinkdbdash)

serverCounts.carbonitex: optional carbonitex key to post to carbonitex.net when in prod
serverCounts.dbots: optional dbots api key to post to bots.discord.pw when in prod
serverCounts.dbotsOrg: optional dbots.org api key to post to discordbots.org when in prod
